descriptionNullable:
Data:
The dataset includes transactional data of bike sales, detailing the date of sale, customer demographics (age and gender), geographical information (country and state), product details, and financial metrics (cost, price, profit, revenue).

Dataset Overview
The dataset contains the following columns:

Date: The date of the sale.
Day: The day of the month.
Month: The month of the sale.
Year: The year of the sale.
Customer_Age: Age of the customer.
Age_Group: Age group category.
Customer_Gender: Gender of the customer.
Country: Country where the sale occurred.
State: State where the sale occurred.
Product_Category: Category of the product sold.
Sub_Category: Sub-category of the product.
Product: Specific product sold.
Order_Quantity: Quantity of the product ordered.
Unit_Cost: Cost per unit of the product.
Unit_Price: Selling price per unit of the product.
Profit: Profit made from the sale.
Cost: Total cost of the order.
Revenue: Total revenue from the sale.
